Pre-Game Insights: Spain has been the standout team since the start of the tournament, topping Group B with a perfect record of nine points.
Spain is the only team to reach the round of 16 without conceding a goal.
Spain's trio of Lamine Yamal, Alvaro Morata, and Nico Williams has been crucial in breaking the German defense.
Germany began Euro 2024 as one of the top favorites to win the tournament.
Germany finished at the top of Group A with seven points and defeated Denmark 2-0 in the round of 16.
Players like Jamal Musiala, Kai Havertz, and Florian Wirtz are in contention for the Golden Boot.
